{"fields":{"body":[{"value":"A great elder of our times has passed on, leaving this parting gift for the world. Wisdom, transcendence, and an opening to life without fear. This inspiring documentary of the American visionary and author Joseph Chilton Pearce is a powerful solution for a world in conflict.\r\n\r\nRevealing ancient wisdom from older cultures, this film uncovers our lost inheritance. Beyond boundaries and above control – this is a journey to transform the very behaviors that are destroying life on earth. Eternity’s Sunrise presents a future without limitations.\r\n\r\nEternity’s Sunrise shatters the myths of traditional education and challenges the very status quo that we take for granted. For over five decades, from Oxford to Harvard University, this wise sage has unravelled humanity’s core problems. In his final interview, at 90 years old, Joseph charismatically presents a movie to open our minds and awaken our heart.\r\n\r\nMapping man’s appetite for control, from the rise of Hitler to modern corporations, this is the compelling story of humanity’s demise. Eternity’s Sunrise is a blueprint for radical change. This massive wake up call is nothing short of a revolutionary call to action.\r\n\r\nJoseph Chilton Pearce changed the very zeitgeist of a generation. Eternity’s Sunrise is a search for meaning in a world lost in greed.","format":1}],"teaser":[{"value":"Joseph Chilton Pearce changed the very zeitgeist of a generation, with his revolutionary vision for reclaiming humanity’s lost inheritance. Eternity’s Sunrise is a search for meaning in a world lost in greed.","format":1}],"series_nid":[{"nid":null}],"season":[{"value":null}],"episode":[{"value":null}],"instructor":[{"value":null}],"director":[{"value":"Stephen Mulhearn"}],"producer":[{"value":"Stephen Mulhearn"}],"writer":[{"value":"Stephen Mulhearn"}],"cast":[{"value":"Stephen Mulhearn, Joseph Chilton Pearce, Thom Hartmann, Karen Pearce, Shakti Pearce, David Tetrault"}],"copyright":[{"value":"2